metadata.dc:description: A white caucasian male 38-year-old has come to our Department with an intramasseterin neoformation. The histopathological report has been angiolymphoid hyperplasia. Surgical approach is discussed considering at the same time the peculiarity of this rare type of intervention.
metadata.dc:title: Un caso raro de hiperplasia angiolinfoide intramaseterina.
[A rare case of angiolymphoid intramasseteric hyperplasia].
